      "title": "Distribute and combine",
      "content": "Distribute $5$ and combine like terms:<br/>$$3x+5(x+4)=76$$<br/>$$3x+5x+20=76$$<br/>$$8x+20=76$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Isolate x",
      "content": "Subtract $20$ from both sides:<br/>$$8x=56$$"
